<title>USA: Vision Sciences needs operating funds.</title>
<headline>Vision Sciences needs operating funds.</headline>
<dateline>NATICK, Mass. 1997-05-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>Vision-Sciences Inc said on Wednesday that it will require additional financing or an alternative means of support during the fiscal year ending March 31, 1998.</p>
<p>The company has continued to fund its operations principally with proceeds from equity financings, it said.</p>
<p>The company expects losses to continue at least through the first two quarters of the fiscal year ending March 31, 1998, it said.</p>
